---
export const prerender = true;

import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy - Zero Fluff"
  description="How Zero Fluff handles your data. Plain English, no legalese."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow stack">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted">
        Here's how we handle your data. No legalese, no small print tricks --
        just a straight answer to what we collect and why.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section reveal">
    <div class="container narrow stack">
      <h2>Who we are</h2>
      <p>
        Zero Fluff is a sole trader consultancy run by Andy Doyle, based in
        Totnes, Devon. If you need to get in touch about anything on this page,
        email <a href="mailto:andy@zerofluff.co.uk">andy@zerofluff.co.uk</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section reveal">
    <div class="container narrow stack">
      <h2>What data we collect</h2>
      <p>
        Your name, email address, and whatever you write in the message field.
        That's it. Nothing else.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section reveal">
    <div class="container narrow stack">
      <h2>How we collect it</h2>
      <p>
        Directly from you, when you submit the contact form on this website. We
        don't collect data any other way -- no cookies, no tracking scripts, no
        analytics.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section reveal">
    <div class="container narrow stack">
      <h2>Why we use it</h2>
      <p>
        To read your message and reply to your enquiry. That's it.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section reveal">
    <div class="container narrow stack">
      <h2>Lawful basis</h2>
      <p>
        Legitimate interests. You contacted us with a business enquiry, and we
        need your details to respond. We're not going to use your data for
        anything else.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section reveal">
    <div class="container narrow stack">
      <h2>Who we share it with</h2>
      <p>
        <a href="https://resend.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Resend</a>
        is our email delivery service. When you submit the contact form, Resend
        processes the submission to deliver it to us. No one else sees your data.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section reveal">
    <div class="container narrow stack">
      <h2>How long we keep it</h2>
      <p>
        12 months after our last communication, then we delete it.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section reveal">
    <div class="container narrow stack">
      <h2>Your rights</h2>
      <p>
        You have the right to:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access your data</li>
        <li>Correct it if it's wrong</li>
        <li>Have it deleted</li>
        <li>Restrict how we use it</li>
        <li>Object to processing</li>
        <li>Request a copy in a portable format</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Email <a href="mailto:andy@zerofluff.co.uk">andy@zerofluff.co.uk</a> and
        we'll sort it out.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section reveal">
    <div class="container narrow stack">
      <h2>How to complain</h2>
      <p>
        Contact us first at
        <a href="mailto:andy@zerofluff.co.uk">andy@zerofluff.co.uk</a>. We'd
        rather fix the problem directly.
      </p>
      <p>
        If we can't resolve it, you can complain to the Information
        Commissioner's Office (ICO) at
        <a href="https://ico.org.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ico.org.uk</a>
        or call 0303 123 1113.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section reveal">
    <div class="container narrow stack">
      <p class="text-sm text-muted">Last updated: March 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
